        "latin": "Yusabbi\u1e25u lill\u0101hi m\u0101 fis-sam\u0101w\u0101ti wa m\u0101 fil-ar\u1e0d(i), lahul-mulku wa lahul-\u1e25amdu wa huwa \u2018al\u0101 kulli syai'in qad\u012br(un).",
